{"tid":607641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G2000反被控侵權　判賠兩千萬","createTime":"2018-03-27T12:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T15:46:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d29ae04d43997f473c9d01dc95817b07f8373e22","tid":607641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180327/20344232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344232&d=12Zo%2FuCTu563fDPCZyjaHf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d1bd22c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20344232&h=36914388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180327/20344232</a><br />\n<br />\nG2000反被控侵權　判賠兩千萬<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】曾在內地捲入商標官司的港區人大代表、實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰表示，香港維他奶集團應盡快到內地商標局向「維他牛」商標提出反對，否則有機會被「維他牛」反告侵權。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰回應《蘋果》指，若內地商標局否決香港維他的投訴，唯一原因相信是兩者分別使用繁體字及簡體字，但投訴被否決很可能對香港維他日後內地業務造成負面影響，亦有機會隨時被「維他牛」反告侵權，香港維他必須審慎處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180327/large/a04b01a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180327%2Flarge%2Fa04b01a.gif&h=3c33c458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田北辰（圓圖）當年先在內地註冊G2000商標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商標局與法院判決不同<br />\n<br />\n創辦時裝品牌G2000的他表示，當年他先在內地註冊G2000的商標，其後內地商人趙華註冊「2000」商標，「我都去咗（內地）商標局反對，但商標局認為我有個G字，人哋冇 ，係河水不犯井水。但我好唔想，被佢搶咗生意」。趙華之後更反告G2000侵權，G2000在2008年被內地法院判敗訴，要向趙華賠償2,000萬元人民幣。田不服上訴，雙方最終和解。<br />\n<br />\n田說，已向直屬國務院的市場管理委員反映商標問題，「𠵱家內地商標局嘅決定同法院嘅判決係兩回事，亦係結構上最大嘅缺陷」。隨後已有官員承諾，日後將在條文寫明，法院就商標侵權的判決需與商標局協調，惟未知條文何時出台。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李詠希<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t報稱工廠基地為外判加工廠<br />\n要聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t侵權案頻生　米高佐敦中招<br />\n要聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t內地山寨「維他牛」似足維他檸檬茶老闆：商標合法　最好來收購<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"f24da4004fa42d0ca50e8a483d192eccd7940a84","tid":607641,"uid":78574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"抵啦田狗"},{"pid":"639f991a4b55c5c992eb00332adccd75227bb560","tid":607641,"uid":887,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"到底係咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我早註冊過你 但係係我抄你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277033fd5c6665eeb83046789cacb056e330ea04","tid":607641,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78482022b41d4ac1873fddc20bbe5c51db1d23a","tid":607641,"uid":73109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1446f263e9ad5f21e6663ad000cea67f990ade2","tid":607641,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639f991a4b55c5c992eb00332adccd75227bb560","tid":607641,"uid":887,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"到底係咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我早註冊過你 但係係我抄你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"其實度度都係咁（好似係）"},{"pid":"bb237f4340be896a704d9a47662686af3860843c","tid":607641,"uid":65333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死, 你都有今日"},{"pid":"c287eaee827fd0454595f7e6c7be96662135ee51","tid":607641,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6be5a1be37d17704957eebdf4a162675be3bedac","tid":607641,"uid":14918,"like":1,"di